Version 0.3
2004-04-18

	* Windows support

	* Allow use of other Java libraries with MakeHeaderModule

Version 0.2.1
2003-07-23

	* Minimal changes to work with GHC 6.0. May not work with 5.04.

Version 0.2
2003-04-11

	* MacOS X support

	* 'Haskell' now a separate Autotools project installing in /usr/lib/jvm-bridge/

	* New array region access functions

	* Correct array types in autogenerated class interfaces

	* Subtype parameters in autogenerated class interfaces

	* VMLayer 'env' parameter now implicit

	* Various changes in the BasicLayer

	* new native StartExecuteFunction function called by getExecuteFunctionClass, defineCallbackClass

Version 0.1
2001-12-16
